---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import PageHero from "../../components/PageHero.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Who We Help"
  description="Support for engineering teams that need reliable PLC and automation capacity."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Who We Help"
    title="Supporting Engineering Teams That Need Reliable Automation Capacity"
    description="We work with companies that need additional PLC and automation engineering support to deliver projects efficiently, without increasing internal headcount."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p>
        Our role is to support existing teams, helping projects move forward smoothly and on time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">Panel Builders</p>
      <h2>Dependable PLC programming and control system support</h2>
      <p>
        We work alongside panel builders to provide PLC programming, HMI development, and control
        system design.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you need support on a single project or ongoing engineering capacity, we integrate
        with your workflow and help you deliver complete, fully functional systems.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">System Integrators</p>
      <h2>Additional engineering support for demanding delivery schedules</h2>
      <p>
        We provide additional engineering support across system design, PLC development, and
        commissioning.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our role is to strengthen your delivery capability, helping you maintain project timelines
        and quality without overloading your internal team.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">Pump &amp; Water System Projects</p>
      <h2>Specialist support for pump and water infrastructure automation</h2>
      <p>
        We contribute specialist knowledge in pump control systems, pressure boosting, wastewater
        applications, and control and protection logic.
      </p>
      <p>
        We typically support these projects as part of a wider team, working alongside panel
        builders, integrators, or contractors to deliver reliable automation systems.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">How We Work</p>
      <h2>A flexible engineering partner that integrates with your team</h2>
      <p>
        We act as a flexible engineering partner, supporting your existing team rather than
        replacing it.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our focus is on clear communication, practical engineering solutions, and reliable project
        delivery.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta-band">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">Support Capacity</p>
      <h2>Additional PLC and automation support when you need it</h2>
      <p>
        If your team needs additional PLC or automation support, we can step in quickly and
        integrate with your existing project workflow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
